  "body_excerpt": "Fluentd provided by Fluentd Project contains multiple vulnerabilities listed below.  <a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/22.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44024\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/306.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44025\" target=\"_blank\"></a>    <a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/409.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44160\" target=\"_blank\"></a>  <a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/918.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44161\" target=\"_blank\"></a>  <a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/409.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44162\" target=\"_blank\"></a>  <a href=\"https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/409.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-44163\" target=\"_blank\"></a><ul><li>Path traversal in ${tag} Placeholder (CWE-22) - CVE-2026-44024</li><li>Missing authentication for critical function in Monitor Agent API (CWE-306) - CVE-2026-44025</li><li>Improper handling of highly compressed data in in_http and in_forward  (CWE-409) - CVE-2026-44160</li><li>Server-side request forgery in out_http (CWE-918) - CVE-2026-44161</li><li>Improper handling of highly compressed data in in_s3 (CWE-409) - CVE-2026-44162</li><li>Improper handling of highly compressed data in in_opentelemetry (CWE-409) - CVE-2026-44163</li></ul>The developer reported these vulnerabilities to IPA to notify users of the solutions through JVN. JPCERT/CC and the developer coordinated under the Information Security Early Warning Partnership.",
